thread.title: BRIEF-Haoxiangni Health Food sees FY 2017 net profit up 157.99 pct to 195.37 pct

author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Haoxiangni Health Food sees FY 2017 net profit up 157.99 pct to 195.37 pct

organizations.name: reuters) - haoxiangni health food co ltd

text:
Jan 31(Reuters) - Haoxiangni Health Food Co Ltd :
* Sees net profit for FY 2017 to increase by 157.99 percent to 195.37 percent, compared to net profit of FY 2016 (39.3 million yuan) * In the previous outlook, the company expected the net profit for FY 2017 to be 101.3 million yuan to 121.0 million yuan
Source text in Chinese: goo.gl/dmJMgr
Further company coverage: 002582.SZ (Beijing Headline News)
